WeAre.Atour: Xarunteena, waxaan aad ugu xiisayneynaa in qalabka elegtarooniga ah uu u shaqeeyo si habsami leh oo hufan. Kooxdayada farsamayaqaannada khabiirada ah iyo xirfadlayaasha iibka waxay u heellan yihiin bixinta dayactirka ugu sarreeya iyo adeegyada iibka dhammaan baahiyahaaga elegtarooniga ah.
